In this branch/day we will be learn how to use assets(present as a part of our app after build) in our app:
* we will also be learning how to play audio from assets and from internet
* in assets to include file and folder we use this syntax:
file : folder/filename
all files in a folder folder/
* adding stay awake permission in mainfest file for audio to play for long time : <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WAKE_LOCK" />
* by default auioplayers takes files from assets folder to get files from other folder provide 'prefix: 'audio/' in AudioCache() contructor as an argument
* AudioPlayer class to play audios from net